{"id": 1764, "genre": 1000, "title": "你也忍不住有这些互联网认知思路吗？", "description": "作为一个独立思考的你，都遇到过哪些看起来没啥问题，但究其根本还是有点问题的互联网思维？（欢迎点开选项看例子）题图来自：Pixabay", "record_count": 5028, "comment_count": 43, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170628110047paXt3LuKfI8lbWc4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-12T17:00:57Z", "questions": [{"id": 2512, "title": "你也忍不住有这些互联网认知思路吗？", "content": "你也忍不住有这些互联网信息认知思路吗？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 216664, "content": "看到一则信息总会跟自己比较，最后只觉得符合自己价值观的有道理", "image": "img/option/option/20170628110209CxAig6UToPFWbDN9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216665, "content": "常常会更愿意转发能使自己产生“优越感”和“我真棒”的文章", "image": "img/option/option/201706281104291y3zrLAeTPpQEDcv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216666, "content": "碰到能支持自己观点、打击到“敌人”的文章就忍不住转发", "image": "img/option/option/20170628110406VZH3eE06d4xDcU5A.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216667, "content": "公共议题会看，但忍不住会想“还好我没有受到伤害”", "image": "img/option/option/20170628110458WbPMhFex4BpUyLd3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216671, "content": "容易像看小说故事一样看新闻，对“反转情节”有迷之期待", "image": "img/option/option/20170628110626PUNoIa48ngwstrO2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216673, "content": "看到富二代、农民工、女司机这样的群体标签就容易说“果然”", "image": "img/option/option/20170628110651CeAubhRWa9wcYzkS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216676, "content": "碰到社会新闻的主要感情：感动或愤怒", "image": "img/option/option/20170628110834DPnQjuHx6gyRIGao.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216678, "content": "我跟社交网络上（加滤镜的）自己一样美！", "image": "img/option/option/20170628110919Rw3bWpUHIFQ62lSV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}